name: Sayla Mass (Gundam) LoRA
description:
The M stands for Massive!

General Info

This LoRA for one of the most classic and iconic characters in the Gundam history has been brought to you through training with the Anything v4.5 model. It allows for a variety of styles and settings depending on your prompt and the model you use. The compatibility with semi-realistic models can be quite impressive and let you create pictures with that classic gundam feel to them.

Usage

The model has been trained using Kohya so you probably want to use it in the same way as you use other Kohya models. If you are Using A1111's Webui you want to move the file into the models>Lora directory. It is very important to use the relevant trigger word so that you can get results that look close to mine or even better. I advise using a weight of 0.6-1.0 but you might even be able to go lower in some cases.
